These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, cola, iced-tea
4 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, ferret, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk | iced-tea | cola |
| Pet        | lizard | cat   | guinea-pig | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, action, drama, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, indian, colombian, pakistani
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4
4. the spanish is the person watching romance movies##1
5. the indian is on the right of the colombian##1
6. the spanish is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | romance  | action  | sports |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | spanish | colombian | indian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pumpkin, peach, cauliflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, action, scientific, time-travel
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | cauliflower | peach | pumpkin    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | time-travel     | mystery | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, camping, puzzles, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, metal, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of classical and the fan of ambient##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games | card-games | camping | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | classical   | country    | ambient  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, pop, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, japanese, pakistani, egyptian
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the japanese is the fan of soul##1
3. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
5. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
6. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | gospel    | pop   | soul       |
| Nationality   | turkish | egyptian | pakistani | japanese |

