3. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
4. the thai is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the dutch is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | thriller | horror | crime |
| Nationality   | american | british     | thai  | dutch  |

