.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, journalist, doctor, lawyer
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, frog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the journalist##3
2. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
4. the lawyer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the mechanic is between the lawyer and the journalist##2
6. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the turtle is between the mechanic and the owner of the frog##2
8. the mechanic is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | journalist | mechanic      | lawyer | doctor |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | chinchilla | turtle    | frog            |

