.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, cherry, tomato, pomegranate
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, chinchilla, pony
1. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the fish and the person eating tomato##2
4. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating tomato is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | pomegranate | cherry   | apricot | tomato |
| Pet    | pony     | fish | lizard     | chinchilla  |

