.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, salsa, reggae, rock
1. the person drinking milk is the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of rock is between the fan of funk and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | fanta   | milk | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa | rock        | funk    |

