.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, climbing, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee   | soy-milk   | iced-tea      | lemonade      |
| Sport      | climbing | volleyball | swimming | handball |

