3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
4. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
5. the person eating onion is between the fan of pop and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lettuce | pepper  | onion  | pear |
| Music-Genre   | house  | country | reggae | pop   |

