.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, fishing, video-games, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, handball, cricket
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | fishing         | baking   | video-games |
| Sport   | handball    | rowing | cricket | rugby   |

