.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, filmmaking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, snowboarding, parkour, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | video-games | filmmaking    | cooking |
| Sport   | golf   | parkour  | climbing | snowboarding     |

