.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, drawing, filmmaking, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, dutch, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
3. the malaysian is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the dutch is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the malaysian is between the mexican and the dutch##2
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | filmmaking | photography | drawing    |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian  | mexican     | indian |

