.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, artichoke, mango, eggplant
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
7. the person eating broccoli is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice    | tea       | coffee |
| Food       | artichoke  | mango | eggplant | broccoli  |

