.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, chinese, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, skateboard, car
1. the argentine is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the chinese##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | dutch | chinese | argentine  | polish |
| Transport     | roller      | skateboard       | jet-ski | car     |

