.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, musician, coach, nurse
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, bus, airplane
1. the musician is in an even position##4
2. the musician is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
3. the person driving the motorbike is between the architect and the person driving the tram##2
4. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the nurse##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | architect | coach   | nurse | musician |
| Transport   | airplane          | motorbike | tram         | bus  |

 